title: American_Top_10_Top_60_Christmas_Songs
description:
"I'm Casey Kasem, and like Jolly Saint Nick, I've got a bag full of gifts, each of them a holiday hit."


This five hour show is a rebroadcast of a countdown show hosted by Casey Kasem subsequent to AT40. The program was called American Top 10.

It was originally broadcast in two parts, on December 17th, and December 24th, 2005.

The following extras from the first half are repeated in the second half:

What Christmas Means To Me - Jessica Simpson
Silver And Gold - Vanessa Williams
Christmas Time - The Backstreet Boys
Where Are You, Christmas? - Faith Hill
The Christmas Shoes - Newsong
The First Noel - Karla Bonoff

Happy Holidays!
